s://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kid-Rock-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kid-Rock-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kid-Rock-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kid-Rock-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kid-Rock-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Kid-Rock">Kid Rock</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普</a>的司法部长提名人帕姆·邦迪会面，针对音乐会门票行业的现状。</p><p>这位演唱《All Summer Long》的歌手在他的 Instagram 官方页面上分享了一张他和邦迪在一起的照片，并解释说他计划与司法部长提名人以及整个政府密切合作，解决当前有关门票购买的问题。</p><p> “与我们即将成为司法部长的 @pambondi 一起分享面包真是一种享受，”他的帖子标题这样开头。 “我期待与她和整个政府合作，帮助解决购买音乐会门票的惨败。我要对机器人、黄牛、场馆、票务公司、经理和艺术家等人开一罐大骂，他们用马粪欺骗公众，这种情况已经持续了几十年，而且只会变得更糟。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDiDKl3Pnen/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="htt